To-Do List
A simple and intuitive To-Do List application that allows users to manage tasks efficiently. This project demonstrates fundamental HTML, CSS, and JavaScript concepts and is designed to be user-friendly with basic functionalities including adding, editing, and deleting tasks.

Features:-
Add Tasks: Input new tasks into the list.
Edit Tasks: Modify existing tasks.
Delete Tasks: Remove tasks from the list.
Responsive Design: Adaptable layout that adjusts to different screen sizes.
Technologies Used
HTML: Structure of the application.
CSS: Styling and layout of the application.
JavaScript: Interactive functionalities such as adding, editing, and deleting tasks.

Usage:-
Enter a Task: Type your task into the input box and click "Add" to add it to the list.
Edit a Task: Click "Edit" next to a task to modify its content.
Delete a Task: Click "Delete" next to a task to remove it from the list.
